  <brief_title>Popliteal Sciatic Nerve Block Catheter Placement for Foot Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Determine the Quality of Sensory and Motor Blockade of Popliteal Sciatic Nerve Block Catheters Placed Under Ultrasound Guidance With and Without Nerve Stimulation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
